{"tid":610802,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府強烈譴責戴耀廷在台灣發表港獨言論","createTime":"2018-03-30T09:45:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-30T09:45:54.000Z","uid":103207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a0e7a63ca862d74c445b8206c9c569c65589214c","tid":610802,"uid":103207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T09:45:54.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】特區<span style=\"color: red;\">政府發言人強烈譴責港大法律系副教授戴耀廷</span>，指<span style=\"color: red;\">他早前在台灣一個活動指香港可以考慮成為獨立國家</span>，是不符合一國兩制及違反基本法。<br />\n<br />\n政府回應傳媒查詢時指，任何有關港獨的主張均不符合一國兩制、基本法以及香港社會整體的長遠利益，對於<span style=\"color: red;\">有大學教員發表有關言論感到震驚，並予以強烈譴責</span>。<br />\n<br />\n戴耀廷於上週六到台灣出席台灣青年反共救國團的活動時，提到民主自決下香港可考慮成為獨立國家。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=300759&amp;home=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D300759%26home%3D1&d=%2Fw6tNE5AmV4a9nGMYKjewUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=22127837\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D300759%26home%3D1&h=190c27da\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=300759&amp;home=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}